  body
    .main-container
      p(style='font-size:85px;margin-top:-85px;padding:20px;color:#ddd;font-family:"Raleway"') Noiseless
        span(style='font-weight:600') AMA
      form(action='ama',method='get')
        input(type='text',placeholder='Enter the URL of the AMA',name='id').main-input
        input(type='submit',value='Remove Noise').main-submit
      p#app-description Read any 
        a(href='http://reddit.com/r/IAmA') reddit AMA
        |  in a clean and simplified Q/A format.
